### 测试 A：密码太短 (应该报错)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/register?confirmPassword=123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test_user",
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "passwordHash": "123"
}

### 测试 B：两次密码不一致 (应该报错)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/register?confirmPassword=654321
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test_user",
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "passwordHash": "123456"
}

### 测试 C：注册成功
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/register?confirmPassword=1238786765
Content-Type: application/json

{
"username": "Wang",
"email": "3213213@qq.com",
"passwordHash": "1238786765"
}

### 测试 D：验证登录功能 (Login Verification)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/login?username=Wang&password=1238786765